Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:50.91,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Láo xược thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.43,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ta sẽ ăn ngươi, đồ quái vật ngọt mát!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:56.15,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mời cả nhà xơi cơm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:03.13,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ủa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:05.01,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ngươi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:09.27,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Không cắt được...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.83,CR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mình...
